\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Part, sections and subsections constitute a document structure which can
 be extracted in the form of a table of content.
 Change a standard text into a title by clicking on the formatting information
 drop down list at the top left of the Lyx screen.
 To insert a table of content click on 
\family sans
